'''不受欢迎的人'''（{{Lang-la|Persona Non Grata}}{{\}}[[複數_(語法)|复数]]：{{lang|la|Personae Non Gratae}}；{{Lang-en|Person Not Welcome}}）是所在国对外国[[外交官|外交官]]有时所施加的一种身份，目的是取消他们免于被[[逮捕|逮捕]]或其他正常诉讼的[[外交豁免权|外交豁免权]]保护。

== 外交领域 ==
根据《[[维也纳外交关系公约|维也纳外交关系公约]]》第九条的规定，接受国可以“随时不具解释”地宣布外交使团的任何成员为不受欢迎的人。<ref name="UN">{{cite web |title=维也纳外交关系公约 |url=https://www.un.org/zh/documents/treaty/files/UNCITRAL-1961.shtml |publisher=[[联合国|联合国]] |accessdate=2021-10-25 |language=zh-hans |date=1961-04-18 |archive-date=2021-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211025160541/https://www.un.org/zh/documents/treaty/files/UNCITRAL-1961.shtml }}</ref><ref name="VanOpdorp">{{cite web |author1=Davis VanOpdorp |title=What does it mean to be declared persona non grata? |url=https://www.dw.com/cda/en/what-does-it-mean-to-be-declared-persona-non-grata/a-47800884 |publisher=[[德国之声|德国之声]] |accessdate=2021-10-25 |language=en |date=2019-06-03 |archive-date=2022-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220408152025/https://www.dw.com/cda/en/what-does-it-mean-to-be-declared-persona-non-grata/a-47800884 }}</ref> 被如此宣布的人是被认为不可接受的，通常会将他或她召回派遣国；如果不召回，接收国可以“拒绝承认该员为使馆人员”。<ref name="UN" /> 一个人甚至可以在他进入该国之前就被宣布为不受欢迎的人。<ref name="VanOpdorp" />

《维也纳公约》第四十一条和第四十二条保护外交使团工作人员视其级别而不因违反接受国[[民法|民法]]和[[刑法|刑法]]而受到起诉，因此他们必须尊重接受国国家法律和条例。而违反这些条款可能会导致使用不受欢迎的人声明来惩罚犯错的使团成员。它还用于驱逐涉嫌[[间谍|间谍]]活动的外交官，被描述为“与外交身份不符的活动”；<ref>{{cite web |author1=William J. Eaton |title=Soviets Oust 5 U.S. Diplomats as Spies : Shultz Promises Action in Response to Unprecedented Mass Expulsion |url=https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1986-10-20-mn-6499-story.html |publisher=[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]] |accessdate=2021-10-25 |language=en |date=1986-10-20 |quote=The Soviet Foreign Ministry accused the five Americans of engaging in "actions which are incompatible with their official status"--the normal diplomatic jargon for espionage. |archive-date=2022-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220412211926/https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1986-10-20-mn-6499-story.html }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Spain-Russia spy row leads to diplomats' expulsion |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-12086186 |website=[[BBC在线|BBC在线]] |publisher=[[BBC新闻|BBC新闻]] |accessdate=2021-10-25 |language=en |date=2012-03-06 |quote=The Spanish foreign ministry spokesman said the two Russians had been expelled "for activities incompatible with their status as diplomats" - the diplomatic term for spying. |archive-date=2022-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220412211856/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-12086186 }}</ref> 或任何公开的犯罪行为，例如[[毒販|贩毒]]。当然，声明也可能象征性地用于表示不满。<ref>{{cite web |author1=Anna Cavell |title='Persona non grata' in South Sudan |url=https://www.aljazeera.com/blogs/africa/2012/11/47543.html |publisher=[[半岛电视台|半岛电视台]] |accessdate=2021-10-25 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160226003127/https://www.aljazeera.com/blogs/africa/2012/11/47543.html |archivedate=2016-02-26 |language=en |date=2012-11-14 |quote="Persona non grata" (PNG), is the most serious form of censure a government can take against a person with diplomatic immunity and often used by governments as symbolic expressions of displeasure.}}</ref>

而当所谓的“[[以牙還牙|针锋相对]]”互相驱逐情况业已发生，卷入其中的各国都会互相宣布对方的外交人员为“不受欢迎的人”并驱逐出境，这在[[冷战|冷战时期]]尤为明显。而在冷战之外的著名互相驱逐事件则是2011年[[美国|美国]]与[[厄瓜多尔|厄瓜多尔]]：由于[[维基解密|维基解密]]泄露了外交电报内容，厄瓜多尔宣布驱逐美国驻该国大使；而作为回应，美国也很快驱逐了厄瓜多尔驻该国大使。<ref>{{cite news |title=US expels Ecuadorian ambassador in diplomatic tit-for-tat |url=https://www.france24.com/en/20110407-ecuador-usa-ambassador-expulsion-over-wikileaks-cable-diplomacy |accessdate=2021-10-25 |work=[[法兰西24|法兰西24]] |agency=[[法新社|法新社]] |language=en |date=2011-07-04 |archive-date=2022-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220412211912/https://www.france24.com/en/20110407-ecuador-usa-ambassador-expulsion-over-wikileaks-cable-diplomacy }}</ref>

== 其他领域 ==
外交官以外的人可以被一个国家宣布为不受欢迎的人。<ref name="VanOpdorp" /> 在非外交领域中，将某人称为不受欢迎的人是指该人不受欢迎或不被他人接受。<ref>{{cite web |title=Persona Non Grata |url=https://dictionary.cambridge.org/us/dictionary/english/persona-non-grata |publisher={{Link-en|剑桥高阶学习词典|Cambridge Advanced Learner's Dictionary}} |accessdate=2021-10-25 |language=en |archive-date=2022-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220412212005/https://dictionary.cambridge.org/us/dictionary/english/persona-non-grata }}</ref>

在[[菲律宾|菲律宾]]，省、城镇和城市的地方立法机关可以宣布某些人或群体——包括非外交官和菲律宾公民——为不受欢迎的人，以通过不具约束力的决议表达对某些人的负面情绪。 这可能是对违反当地法令或法律的人的回应。

